code: export function getAllDocumentParents(document,items){var getParent=function getParent(document){return items.find(function(item){return item.uuid===document.parentUuid;});};var currentDocument=document;var parents=[];while(currentDocument&&currentDocument.parentUuid){var parent=getParent(currentDocument);if(parent){parents.push(parent);}currentDocument=parent;}return parents;}
